    <section class="api-section" id="bot-faq">
        <header>
            <h2>FAQ / Funding / Policy API</h2>
            <span class="api-pill method-get">GET</span>
            <span class="api-pill scope-public">Public · API-key gated</span>
        </header>
        <p>Static knowledge base of SG funding schemes (SkillsFuture, WSQ, UTAP, PSEA, MCES, IBF, SFEC, Absentee Payroll) and policy topics (cancellation, certificates, assessments, corporate registration). Returns ALL topics in one response — the bot does keyword matching locally.</p>

        <div class="note"><strong>Content is editorial.</strong> Edit <code>app/code/local/MMD/Courses/controllers/Api/FaqController.php</code> to add/update topics. Each topic includes a <code>keywords</code> array the bot uses for matching.</div>

        <h3>Endpoint</h3>
        <pre class="url-block">GET <?php echo $this->htmlEscape($prodBaseUrl); ?>/courses/api_faq</pre>

        <h3>Response shape (per topic)</h3>
        <pre>{
  "id": "skillsfuture-credit",
  "title": "SkillsFuture Credit (SFC)",
  "keywords": ["skillsfuture", "sfc", "credit", "$500", "claim", "subsidy"],
  "summary": "Every Singapore Citizen aged 25+ receives a $500 SkillsFuture Credit...",
  "eligibility": "Singapore Citizens aged 25 and above...",
  "how_to_claim": ["Browse approved courses...", "Add to cart...", "..."],
